with educators to create

00:25:07.720 --> 00:25:09.430
this common
curriculum that we'll

00:25:09.430 --> 00:25:14.220
offer for free for schools
that commit to teach it.

00:25:14.220 --> 00:25:17.040
And we'll even provide
them incentives or tools,

00:25:17.040 --> 00:25:18.570
