So what has been your take on
the whole organic movement?

00:36:54.390 --> 00:36:56.250
And is that something that
might be in the works?

00:36:56.250 --> 00:36:57.083
DANIEL LUBETZKY: No.

00:36:57.083 --> 00:37:00.280
I mean, we think about these
questions all the time.

00:37:00.280 --> 00:37:05.270
For us, we needed to choose what
we're going to be as a brand.

00:37:05.270 --> 00:37:08.630
And what we chose is to provide
people nutritionally rich,

00:37:08.630 --> 00:37:10.110
premium ingredients.

00:37:10.110 --> 00:37:14.530
And in our particular
categories where we play,

00:37:14.530 --> 00:37:16.920
we felt that was what was
most important and most

00:37:16.920 --> 00:37:18.600
differentiated for us to add.

00:37:18.600 --> 00:37:23.412
And you know, I respect a
lot of other fair trade,

00:37:23.412 --> 00:37:25.120
organic, other things
that are important.

00:37:25.120 --> 00:37:29.390
We try to behave
environmentally responsibly.

00:37:29.390 --> 00:37:31.830
We're doing a whole 360
