00:37:52.790 --> 00:37:55.770
and treat the product
with a lot of respect.

00:37:55.770 --> 00:37:57.230
And so we needed
to choose what was

00:37:57.230 --> 00:38:00.590
the most important thing for
us to provide to the consumer.

00:38:00.590 --> 00:38:03.460
There's also an issue
