dangerous the situation is.

00:38:20.360 --> 00:38:22.530
I was alluding to
scarcity of food.

00:38:22.530 --> 00:38:24.240
It's a very serious problem.

00:38:24.240 --> 00:38:26.610
There's huge drought
problems in California.

00:38:26.610 --> 00:38:31.435
There's bee collapse
challenges that are finally

00:38:31.435 --> 00:38:32.310
