years has been so challenged.

00:38:39.160 --> 00:38:42.260
And in the meantime,
consumption is skyrocketing.

00:38:42.260 --> 00:38:43.930
So that's why these
things are becoming

00:38:43.930 --> 00:38:45.550
more and more expensive.

00:38:45.550 --> 00:38:48.540
And as we're going to need to
feed 2 billion more people,

00:38:48.540 --> 00:38:50.400
there's a lot of questions
that as a society

00:38:50.400 --> 00:38:51.890
we need to ask
ourselves about how

00:38:51.890 --> 00:38:54.450
we're going to be feeding all
of those 2 billion people.

00:38:54.450 --> 00:38:56.390
Right now what our
team is obsessing about

00:38:56.390 --> 00:39:02.250
is being able to even
source quality products

00:39:02.250 --> 00:39:03.530
on a sustainable basis.

00:39:03.530 --> 00:39:08.280
So there's a lot of questions
that we're challenged with,

00:39:08.280 --> 00:39:10.490
try to balance.

00:39:10.490 --> 00:39:12.580
As a brand, we want to
just continue always

00:39:12.580 --> 00:39:17.940
being nutrition-rich ingredients
that you can see and pronounce.

